<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240527/1716799157912074538.png" title="1716799157912074538.png" alt="图片.png" style="width: 800px; height: 519px;" width="800" height="519"/><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; caret-color: red;">为传播先锋文化和井冈山校区创业精神，激发我校学子对于英语学习及创新和创业的无限热情。公共课教学部主办了我校井冈山校区宣传片英语配音大赛，在此次比赛中，经管学子踊跃参与，在全校近40份精彩投稿中，经过层层筛选和激烈比拼，我院5名优秀选手脱颖而出，晋级总决赛。经管学子在总决赛赛场中展现出卓越风姿，取得了优异成绩！&nbsp;<br/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240527/1716799245738049329.jpg" title="1716799245738049329.jpg" alt="f90edd5828c9579c2089b0dbf8e6f39b.jpg" style="width: 816px; height: 681px;" width="816" height="681"/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240527/1716799291827021072.jpg" title="1716799291827021072.jpg" alt="d78b2a198fbfe4f8ec5ab2ef5ead6fd1.jpg" style="width: 818px; height: 498px;" width="818" height="498"/><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; caret-color: red;">井冈山校区宣传片英语配音大赛中，我院参赛学生出色的表现，在竞赛中脱颖而出，展现出经管积极争先的学院风貌。在此，</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; caret-color: red;">我们对取得佳绩的学生表示热烈的祝贺！希望我院学子在未来的道路上继续前行，不断超越自我，创造更加辉煌的明天。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>